{
  "doc_id": "2574",
  "text": "Research in the cognitive style domain appears to have reached an \"impasse\" (Kozhevnikov, 2007, p. 464) and is currently \"dormant\" [CITATION_1] ; our findings are certainly not making the situation more optimistic. Although tempting, our intention is not to call for a moratorium on this line of research. Perhaps research on style constructs will be wound down if our results are replicated in larger-scale settings.",
